[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0905","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0905.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1052","title":"Microsoft FrontPage 表单结果文件信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft FrontPage 默认将表单提交结果存储在网站根目录下的 `/_private/form_results.txt` 文件中，该文件权限设置为世界可读且位于 Web 文档根目录内，导致任何能够访问该网站的远程攻击者无需身份认证即可直接通过浏览器读取其他用户提交的敏感表单数据（如密码、个人信息等）。此漏洞危害中等，影响使用 Microsoft FrontPage 创建的网站。缓解措施包括更改默认存储路径或限制该文件的访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1052"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.350","remediation":"将 FrontPage 表单结果存储路径从默认的 `/_private/` 目录修改为 Web 根目录之外的路径（如 `C:\\fp_formdata\\`），并通过 IIS 权限设置拒绝匿名用户对 `form_results.txt` 的读取权限。如使用 Apache，在 `.htaccess` 中添加 `<FilesMatch \"form_results\\.txt\"> Deny from all</FilesMatch>` 规则。建议迁移至更新的 Web 开发平台（如 ASP.NET/PHP），因 FrontPage 已停止维护。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93582550911564&w=2","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1052.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1052.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1052","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1052.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1052.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1052.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8552-5cm2-7wch/GHSA-8552-5cm2-7wch.json","https://github.com/ivanitlearning/CTF-Repos/blob/b5364388a861fc7457409d494a9d075d73e7867e/Vulnhub/SkyTower/Web-scan.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88081/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1052.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0905.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0905.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0905.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0904","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0904.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0618","title":"Unix rexec 服务权限提升漏洞","description":"rexec（远程执行）服务是一种未加密的远程命令执行协议，运行在 TCP 512 端口，使用主机名和 .rhosts 文件进行基于主机的认证。攻击者可通过伪造信任主机 IP 地址或利用 .rhosts 配置缺陷绕过认证，在目标系统上以当前用户权限执行任意命令，实现权限提升。该服务默认不启用加密，明文传输密码，容易被中间人攻击窃听。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，建议禁用 rexec 服务并改用 SSH。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0618"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.510","remediation":"立即禁用 rexec 服务（通常为 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 exec 行或 systemctl stop rexec），并使用 SSH（OpenSSH）替代所有远程执行需求。检查系统是否仍在运行 rexecd/in.rexecd 进程并予以停止卸载。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0618","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0618.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0618","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0618.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0618.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0618.json","https://github.com/DefectDojo/django-DefectDojo/blob/619e5656f308396a3cc3a7f039c6426ae98baa17/unittests/scans/openvas/many_vuln.xml","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/rexecd.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jw99-fq4j-hx93/GHSA-jw99-fq4j-hx93.json","https://github.com/ornl-sava/nv/blob/8cbf2a775f3c35accff96fe30217e9afff65410e/data/metasploitable.2.0.nbe","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0618.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0904.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0903","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0903.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1051","title":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 脚本的默认配置存在目录限制缺陷，仅对 /etc/ 目录进行了访问限制，未对其他目录做有效过滤。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过 reply_message_attach 参数指定任意文件路径，导致服务器上任意文件被读取，包括配置文件、源码等敏感信息。该漏洞影响使用默认配置部署 FormHandler.cgi 的 Web 服务器，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1051"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.223","remediation":"立即删除或停用 FormHandler.cgi 脚本，该脚本已不再维护且存在设计缺陷。如必须使用，编辑脚本源码，将附件的基路径硬编码为固定安全目录（如 /var/lib/formhandler/attachments/），并严格校验 reply_message_attach 参数值，拒绝包含 \"../\" 等路径回溯字符的输入。同时配置 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）限制 CGI 目录下仅允许 POST 方法访问该脚本，禁止直接通过 GET 参数读取任意路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34939","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1051.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1051","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1051.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1051.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1051.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6vh4-w25v-6gh9/GHSA-6vh4-w25v-6gh9.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88494/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1051.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0903.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0901","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0901.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1050","title":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 2.0 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Matt Wright 开发的 FormHandler.cgi 2.0 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 reply_message_attach 参数传入 ../ 等路径穿越序列，或直接指定模板文件名为目标文件路径，从而读取服务器上的任意敏感文件。该漏洞影响 FormHandler.cgi 2.0 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1050"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.070","remediation":"建议立即从 Web 服务器中移除或停用 `FormHandler.cgi` 脚本，改用受支持的上传组件。若无法移除，可在 Perl 脚本入口处增加路径规范化校验：使用 `File::Spec->rel2abs` 解析真实路径并检查是否越界到 Web 根目录之外；同时过滤用户输入中的 `..` 和 `/` 字符，并设置严格的模板白名单。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34600","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34939","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/798","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/799","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3550","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19620","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1050","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1050.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rrx8-7p59-h436/GHSA-rrx8-7p59-h436.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/F/formhandler.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/798/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000873.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0901.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0900","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0900.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0822","title":"Qualcomm Qpopper 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Qpopper (qpop) 3.0/3.0b20 版本中存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 AUTH 命令发送特制的超长认证参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Qualcomm qpopper 3.0 及 3.0b20 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0822"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.833","remediation":"升级 Qpopper 至 3.1 或更高版本（该漏洞已在 3.1 中修复），或安装 Qualcomm 官方提供的补丁。如无法升级，在 inetd/xinetd 配置中禁用 POP3 服务或将 qpopper 替换为 Dovecot 等仍在维护的 POP3/IMAP 服务器。利用防火墙限制对 TCP 端口 110 的访问，仅允许受信任的客户端 IP 连接。在代码层面，对 AUTH 命令的输入长度做严格校验（限制缓冲区边界），避免栈溢出。鉴于 Qpopper 已停止维护，强烈建议迁移至 Dovecot 作为邮件接收服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/830","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19646"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0900.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0899","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0899.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0616","title":"TFTP 服务开放导致信息泄露风险","description":"该CVE条目已被官方驳回（REJECT），原描述为\"TFTP服务正在运行\"。TFTP协议使用UDP 69端口，缺乏认证与加密机制，若未配置适当访问控制，运行中的TFTP服务可能被未经授权的攻击者利用进行文件读写操作，导致敏感信息泄露或任意文件上传。但由于该问题属于安全配置范畴而非代码层面的直接安全漏洞，因此不适用CVE编号体系，更适合归入CCE（通用配置枚举）管理。建议在非必要环境中禁用TFTP服务或限制访问来源。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0616"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.373","remediation":"若业务不需要 TFTP 服务，建议在系统中停止并禁用 tftpd/tftp-hpa 服务（如 `systemctl disable tftp` 或移除 xinetd 配置）。如需使用，通过 iptables/firewalld 限制源 IP 访问 UDP 端口 69，仅允许受信任的管理网段连接，并考虑迁移至 SFTP/SCP 等加密文件传输协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0616.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0616","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0616.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/tftpd_detect.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0616.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000453.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/tftpd_detect.nasl","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0616.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0899.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0897","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0897.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1047","title":"BSDI Gauntlet 安全绕过漏洞","description":"BSDI 为 Gauntlet 5.0 防火墙提供的安全补丁若未按正确顺序安装，将导致防火墙访问控制规则失效，远程攻击者可绕过防火墙的访问限制直接访问受保护的内部网络资源。同时，该漏洞还会导致防火墙无法记录绕过攻击的日志，使得攻击行为难以被追溯和检测。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1047"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:35.700","remediation":"确保按 BSDI 官方文档指定的正确顺序安装 Gauntlet 5.0 补丁，先安装内核补丁再安装防火墙组件补丁。若无法确认顺序，建议卸载后按依赖关系重新安装所有补丁：先安装 BSDI OS 基础补丁，再安装 Gauntlet 补丁包。由于该产品已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的防火墙方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94026690521279&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94036662326185&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/3397.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1047.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1047","https:/