son","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0615","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Felix-sec/VulnDataExtr/blob/1f4ecda04291a8a4eb7e49189a9ee2bc026b8389/exact_keywords.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/aboutcode-org/aboutcode-mirror-euvd/blob/1b758e4b71978ff973a6df1bc69fc70b932735fb/advisories/2000/02/EUVD-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0896.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0895","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0895.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0614","title":"通用 FTP 服务运行配置问题","description":"CVE-1999-0614 候选编号已被官方拒绝使用。该条目原始描述仅指出 FTP 服务正在运行，属于系统配置管理范畴，而非独立的安全漏洞。此类配置问题更适合在通用配置枚举（CCE）框架中收录，不具备传统的攻击向量、利用条件或安全影响。因此该编号不应被用于描述任何安全缺陷，也不构成对系统机密性、完整性和可用性的直接威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0614"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.310","remediation":"如非业务必要，建议关闭 FTP 服务（systemctl disable vsftpd/proftpd 或移除对应软件包）；如必须使用，应替换为 SFTP/FTPS 等加密传输协议，并配置防火墙仅允许受信 IP 访问（如 iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 21 -s 信任网段 -j ACCEPT），同时限制匿名登录、禁用 root 账户直接 FTP 登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0614.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0614","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0614.json","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/FTP%20server%20detection.plugin","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0614.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000451.txt","https://github.com/athiasjerome/XORCISM/blob/327e2a3be196660f82c89ae9d7c4e7abe4785b0d/SOURCES/XProviderQualys/QualysSampleResults.xml","https://github.com/Planet-Source-Code/marc-ruef-attack-tool-kit-3-0__1-57240/blob/96061f959b3cf8ad81fa5d603944798cc9f3304c/atk-3.0src/plugins/Macintosh%20OS%20X%20FTP%20server%20detection.plugin"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0895.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0894","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0894.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0613","title":"Sun RPC rpc.sprayd 服务本地权限提升漏洞","description":"rpc.sprayd 是 Unix 系统中用于网络喷发测试的 RPC 服务，运行于 100012 端口。由于 sprayd 守护进程以 root 权限运行且未对调用来源进行充分权限校验，本地攻击者可通过发送特制的 RPC 请求触发 sprayd 命令执行，将自身权限提升至 root。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris、HP-UX 及其他运行 rpc.sprayd 服务的类 Unix 系统，攻击者需拥有目标系统的本地 shell 访问权限。建议在非必要环境下禁用该服务或配置 RPC 访问控制列表。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0613"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.303","remediation":"立即禁用 rpc.sprayd 服务：在 Solaris 中执行 `svcadm disable svc:/network/rpc/spray:default` 或从 inetd.conf 中注释 sprayd 行并重启 inetd。同时配置防火墙/TCP Wrapper 限制 RPC 端口（111/32771-32800）仅允许可信网段访问，并安装操作系统厂商提供的 RPC 安全补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0613","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0613.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0613.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0613","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0613.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0613.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0613.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0613.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0894.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0893","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0893.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1043","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.0/5.5 NNTP 和 SMTP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange 5.0 和 5.5 版本在处理畸形的 NNTP（网络新闻传输协议）数据或 SMTP（简单邮件传输协议）数据时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标邮件服务器发送特制的畸形数据包触发服务进程错误，导致 Exchange 服务崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Exchange Server 5.0 和 5.5，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1043"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:35.187","remediation":"将 Microsoft Exchange Server 升级至 5.5 Service Pack 3（SP3）或更高版本（Exchange 5.0 用户需先迁移至 5.5 再安装 SP3）。如无法升级，可在服务器管理中禁用 NNTP 虚拟服务器服务，并在防火墙策略中限制 TCP 25（SMTP）和 TCP 119（NNTP）端口的访问来源为可信 IP 段。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-007","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1043.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1043","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1043.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1043.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1043.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hjv9-q8gw-pmgm/GHSA-hjv9-q8gw-pmgm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88091/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1043.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0893.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0892","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0892.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0612","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 Finger 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统默认安装的 finger 服务存在信息泄露漏洞。finger 协议设计上未对请求来源进行任何认证或限制，允许网络上的任何攻击者向目标主机的 finger 服务（默认端口 79）发送查询请求，从而获取系统上有效的用户名列表及其他用户账户信息。攻击者可利用收集到的有效用户名进行后续的口令猜测、暴力破解或社会工程学攻击，进一步威胁系统安全。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 等版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0612"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.177","remediation":"停止 Finger 服务（运行 services.msc，找到 \"Finger Service\" 设置为禁用），并在防火墙层面屏蔽 TCP 端口 79 以阻止外部访问。如需使用 finger 功能，应升级到不再内置该服务的 Windows XP 或更高版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0612","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0612.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0612.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0612","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0612.json","https://github.com/Indie365/cbl-mariner/blob/80d864c0a617439675510c037c8a4589aa596fbb/SPECS/finger/CVE-1999-0612.nopatch","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0612.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/324.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0612.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8873-vgfq-r935/GHSA-8873-vgfq-r935.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/finger.rules"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0892.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0891","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0891.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0611","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表键值配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中存在关键注册表项权限配置不当的安全漏洞。该漏洞允许远程攻击者利用不恰当的注册表键值，在目标系统上执行未授权操作，可能导致系统信息泄露、权限提升或拒绝服务。由于受影响注册表项涉及系统核心功能，攻击者一旦利用成功可完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响了 Windows NT 4.0 等早期版本，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0611"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.057","remediation":"检查注册表键 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\ 下关键子键的值权限，将不当值修改为默认安全配置；同时安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全更新，限制对注册表的远程访问权限，仅允许授权管理员通过 ACL 进行修改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0611","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0611.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0611.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0611","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0611.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0611.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0611.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0611.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86267/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0891.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0890","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0890.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1042","title":"Cisco Resource Manager 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cisco Resource Manager (CRM) 1.0 和 1.1 版本存在信息泄露漏洞。由于程序创建的日志文件及临时文件权限设置为全局可读，本地攻击者可利用该缺陷读取这些文件，从而获取用户ID、密码及SNMP团体字符串等敏感凭据信息。此漏洞影响CRM 1.0和1.1版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，CVSS评分1.2，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1042"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:35.067","remediation":"升级 Cisco Resource Manager 至 1.2 或更高版本以修复默认文件权限问题；对手动创建的日志目录和临时文件目录执行 chmod 600 或 640，仅允许 CRM 服务账户读写；通过文件系统 ACL 限制本地非授权用户访问 /var/log/crm 及临时目录；定期审计日志文件权限配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/crmtmp-pub.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1042","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1042.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qqff-qxc6-9qw5/GHSA-qqff-qxc6-9qw5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87012/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0890.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0889","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0889.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1035","title":"Microsoft IIS HTTP GET 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 及 4.0 版本（x86 和 Alpha 平台）在处理畸形的 HTTP GET 请求时存在缺陷，远程未经认证的攻击者可向目标 Web 服务器发送特制的 GET 请求，导致 IIS 服务进程挂起，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程触发，影响运行 IIS 3.0/4.0 的 Windows NT 系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。官方建议升级至更高版 IIS 版本或部署安全补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1035"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:34.207","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS98-019 提供的对应平台热修补丁（IIS 3.0/4.0 for x86/Alpha），或升级到 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 更高版本。由于 IIS 3.0 和 4.0 均已停止技术支持多年，强烈建议迁移至现代受支持的操作系统及 IIS 版本（如 Windows Server 2022 + IIS 10），从根本上消除此漏洞风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q192/2/96.asp","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-019","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1823","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d